flowchart LR
subgraph Client[User & UI]
U[User]
FE[Web UI / Chat]
U --> FE
end


FE -->|/chat| GW[API Gateway]


subgraph Orchestrator[LangGraph Orchestrator]
P[Planner (SLM)]
EVD[Evidence Fan‑out]
PG[Policy Guard]
G[SQL Generator (SLM→LLM)]
EX[Executor (RO + EXPLAIN)]
V[Verifier (SLM)]
R[Refiner (bounded loop)]
AC[Answer Composer]
end


GW --> P
P --> EVD


subgraph Tools[Evidence Producers]
SR[SchemaRetriever\n(Azure AI Search index of catalog)]
CS[ColumnStats\n(precomp / quick SQL)]
GL[BizGlossary\n(Purview/Glossary index)]
SN[ExampleQueries\n(approved SQL library)]
end


EVD --> SR
EVD --> CS
EVD --> GL
EVD --> SN


SR --> EVD
CS --> EVD
GL --> EVD
SN --> EVD


EVD --> PG
PG -->|allow| G
PG -->|block| AC


subgraph DataPlane[Read‑only Data Plane]
RO[(DB Read‑Only Replica)]
LOGS[(Telemetry / OpenTelemetry)]
end


G --> EX
EX --> RO
RO --> EX
EX --> V
V -->|ok| AC
V -->|issues| R
R --> G


AC --> GW
GW --> FE


